# CODEOWNERS — Nexus Anime
#
# GitHub uses this file to assign reviewers automatically when a PR touches
# files matching the listed patterns. Rules are evaluated top-to-bottom; the
# last matching pattern wins.
#
# Keep this file in sync with the team roster. When ownership changes, update
# the entry and open a PR — do not edit `main` directly.
#
# Format:
#   <pattern>    <user-or-team> [<user-or-team> ...]
#
# Patterns follow gitignore-style globbing:
#   *            any characters (except /)
#   **           any characters (including /)
#   ?            any single character
#   [char-set]   one of the characters in the set
#   !pattern     negates a previous pattern
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# --- Fallback owners (catch-all) ---
# Every file in the repo is owned by the core team. More specific rules below
# narrow ownership for sub-areas.
* @nexus-anime/core

# --- Applications ---
# The web app is owned by the frontend team. Any PR touching apps/web
# requires sign-off from someone on that team.
/apps/web/                                                          @nexus-anime/frontend

# --- Packages ---
# Shared libraries are owned by the platform team. Breaking changes to any
# @nexus/* package require platform-team sign-off.
/packages/ui/                                                          @nexus-anime/design-system
/packages/db/                                                          @nexus-anime/platform
/packages/cache/                                                       @nexus-anime/platform
/packages/config-eslint/                                               @nexus-anime/platform

# --- Tooling & CI ---
# Docker, scripts, and GitHub workflows are owned by the platform team.
/tooling/docker/                                                    @nexus-anime/platform
/tooling/scripts/                                                    @nexus-anime/platform
/.github/                                                            @nexus-anime/platform

# --- Documentation ---
# Docs are owned by the docs team, with the core team as a fallback.
/docs/                                                               @nexus-anime/docs @nexus-anime/core

# --- Root config files ---
# Root-level configuration (package.json, turbo.json, prettier, eslint, etc.)
# is owned by the platform team because changes here affect every workspace
# member.
/package.json                                                        @nexus-anime/platform
/pnpm-workspace.yaml                                                 @nexus-anime/platform
/turbo.json                                                          @nexus-anime/platform
/.prettierrc                                                        @nexus-anime/platform
/.prettierignore                                                     @nexus-anime/platform
/tsconfig.base.json                                                  @nexus-anime/platform
/.nvmrc                                                              @nexus-anime/platform
/.env.example                                                        @nexus-anime/platform
/.gitignore                                                          @nexus-anime/platform
/.gitattributes                                                      @nexus-anime/platform
/.editorconfig                                                       @nexus-anime/platform

# --- Security-sensitive files ---
# Changes to the security policy or CI workflows that gate merges should be
# reviewed by the core team.
/SECURITY.md                                                          @nexus-anime/core
/.github/workflows/ci.yml                                            @nexus-anime/core @nexus-anime/platform
/.github/workflows/release.yml                                       @nexus-anime/core @nexus-anime/platform

# --- Repository bootstrap files ---
# The repository constitution and roadmap are owned by the core team.
/REPOSITORY-DESIGN.md                                                @nexus-anime/core
/ROADMAP.md                                                           @nexus-anime/core
/CHANGELOG.md                                                        @nexus-anime/core
/CONTRIBUTING.md                                                     @nexus-anime/core
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                                                  @nexus-anime/core
/SUPPORT.md                                                          @nexus-anime/core
/CODEOWNERS                                                          @nexus-anime/core
/LICENSE                                                             @nexus-anime/core
/README.md                                                           @nexus-anime/core @nexus-anime/docs
